Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.81,0:22:59.34,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.02,0:23:04.02,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}Around That Time, Valtos Was...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.78,0:23:03.37,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,Around That Time, Valtos Was...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.45,0:23:05.77,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,Back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.77,0:23:09.53,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,This is the magic stone that \NHeath failed to retrieve...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.53,0:23:13.17,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,To think it was here... \NAnd we finally have—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.09,0:23:17.20,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.11,0:23:23.08,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.57,0:23:25.42,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.91,0:23:32.01,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.01,0:23:33.09,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Valtos!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.54,0:23:36.29,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,I've obtained what we came here for.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.64,0:23:41.84,main,Who,0000,0000,0000,,I have a bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.84,0:23:43.31,main,Who,0000,0000,0000,,Something bad is going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.84,0:23:49.65,main,who,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on {\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 91: \N"Mereoleona vs. Raia the Disloyal."
